data.title: October Temperatures in the United Kingdom
data.meta_description: Average October temperatures for places throughout the United Kingdom, including lists of monthly high and low temperatures in degrees Celsius and Fahrenheit.
data.text:
Average temperatures for October at cities and towns throughout the United Kingdom are listed below in degrees Celsius and Fahrenheit.

The tables give the normals for maximum and minimum daily temperatures based on weather data collected from 1991 to 2020.

Across the UK, October temperatures average a daily high of 13 degrees Celsius (56 degrees Fahrenheit) and a low of 6 °C (44 °F).
